<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٩٧٢ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(عه)</span> : كَانَ جِدَارُ الْمَسْجِدِ عِنْدَ الْمِنْبَرِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">عه فِي الصَّلاةِ:</span> ثنا ابْنُ الْجُنَيْدِ , وَأَبُو أُمَيَّةَ , بِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>